{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This <strong>free demo</strong> of Echoes of Adventure  lets you try out a few levels to grasp the game's unique mechanics in a familiar 2.5D puzzle platformer fashion. Navigate the level with each character and their special abilities but be careful. What helps you now, might hinder you later.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join Tamo, Mukao, and Cenali on their Adventure and help them face the consequences of their own actions!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your character to start each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528260/extras/ChooseCharacter.gif?t=1739999265\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each of the characters have a unique set of abilities that will help you to navigate through the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528260/extras/UseSpecialAbilities.gif?t=1739999265\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be careful when you use your abilities. They might help you now but could stop you in the next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528260/extras/BlockCharacters.gif?t=1739999265\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo offers a <strong>taste</strong> of the full experience, giving you a chance to strategize, experiment, and solve puzzles in a new way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ready to take on the challenge? Try it now and see if you can master the temple!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3528260?t=1739999265","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3528260?t=1739999265","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s